Advocacy; 
Managing and leading small and large teams; 
Advising Board's and Senior Leaders on contentious matters;
Negotiations on all levels particularly those involving Unions; 
Dispute Resolution; 
Time Management; 
Motivational Speaking; 
Leadership Training; 
Change Management; 
Managing Contract interpretations and negotiations; 
Policy design and management; Problem solving; and
Public speaking.

